{"tid":843471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國客搶先霸靚位露營：因知道稍後會來許多同胞","createTime":"2018-10-01T07:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T12:05:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fe41e290abbbe306c480aafe4d708519292d75f7","tid":843471,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181001/large/1538375161_8775.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181001%2Flarge%2F1538375161_8775.png&h=ed49427a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十一黄金周，不少市民和內地遊客都會趁假期露營度假。香港早前受山竹吹襲，郊野公園遍布塌樹枯枝，記者今午到西貢灣仔營區視察，發現有塌樹壓著石枱，亦有連根吹倒的樹木卧在營地，但仍無礙遊人享受露營樂趣。<br />\n<br />\n來自廣州、與家人露營的江太表示，過去幾年十一黃金周都會來西貢灣仔露營，今年更已來了3次。江太稱，今次在黄金周首天便搶先到灣仔營區設營，因為知道稍後會有許多內地同胞會選擇同一個地點露營度假，來早一步可選擇近海邊營地，方便浮潛暢泳。<br />\n<br />\n江太又指，今次準備度假一個星期，大讚西貢灣仔營區交通方便、有洗手間和浴室，清潔工人亦勤於清理環境，加上感覺比國內更安全，故和家人來享受大自然。<br />\n<br />\n羅先生亦帶同年幼女兒和朋友莫先生，特别選擇在塌樹旁露營。他們表示感覺另有情趣，只是夜深人靜有野豬出來覓食，三更半夜下了一埸秋雨，加上大批內地營友陸續殺到，所以還是早點收拾撤走。<br />\n<br />\n有團體組織親子活動，請來認可機構在灣仔營區，利用樹木安裝飛索。安裝飛索的Brain說，颱風吹襲後有不少樹木受損，因此必須小心選擇適合穩固的樹木安裝飛索確保安全。<br />\n營友阿倫與太太離營前拍照留念，他說感覺還算安全，難得有個新景點；亦有長期在灣仔露營的營友說，明天才是內地遊客來露營的高峰期。過去兩天露營的主要是本港居民。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181001/large/1538375156_323f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181001%2Flarge%2F1538375156_323f.jpg&h=d28b80ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181001/large/1538375159_23a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181001%2Flarge%2F1538375159_23a0.jpg&h=145a72b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181001/large/1538378018_5cf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181001%2Flarge%2F1538378018_5cf4.jpg&h=10d54d63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181001/large/1538376796_d2d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181001%2Flarge%2F1538376796_d2d0.jpg&h=27b36fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181001/58743717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181001%2F58743717&d=nlBVOU48iSINXS0LVaR%2FY3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=14cca66a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181001%2F58743717&h=cca91a70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181001/58743717</a>"},{"pid":"006e135b250b25013aea27d301c8813d42ea9c1c","tid":843471,"uid":23479,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:32:29.000Z","msg":"組團去打Wargame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ea7d9e5380b1a1e95b938645fb6eab2476ee42","tid":843471,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:54:21.000Z","msg":"香港人連露營都被搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287fceefc541a03724f84fe8c9fdcb1d21ef4bf1","tid":843471,"uid":24730,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T08:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/01/160012_38e38a62b1a97e38b6744192de217778.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2F160012_38e38a62b1a97e38b6744192de217778.png&h=a573f6f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n霸完位即刻痾屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e0e5d91131d56e585f07c8f4b51e22518496a2","tid":843471,"uid":530